Since updating to version 3.0.2 from 3.0.0 I am seeing an issue where all file upload directives are firing twice, so events are being added twice, as are input boxes.

I had a dig through the angular code and it seems to be due to angular registering both angularFileUpload and ngFileUpload - this seems to be related to a commit the other day where;

var ngFileUpload = angular.module('ngFileUpload', []);

for (key in angularFileUpload) {
	ngFileUpload[key] = angularFileUpload[key];
}

was added in.

What can be done to alleviate this problem?

